  <brief_title>Measurement of Individual Level of Abortion Stigma Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Measurement of Individual-Level Abortion Stigma Resulting From Pennsylvania State-Mandated Abortion Consent Language: A Pilot Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
